    helpText: 'Many chronic conditions benefit from specialized expertise that goes beyond general care, especially when standard treatments are not providing adequate symptom control. Research specialists who focus specifically on your condition and have experience with complex cases or treatment-resistant symptoms. Prepare a detailed summary of your current treatments, their effectiveness, and specific areas where you need better symptom management before the consultation to maximize the value of this specialized assessment.'
  },
  {
    id: 'prompt-49',
    prompt: 'Create a comprehensive legal and financial protection plan including disability insurance review, medical directives, and chronic illness-specific estate planning',
    category: 'planning',
    helpText: 'Protecting your financial and legal interests becomes crucial when managing a chronic illness that may impact your earning capacity or decision-making abilities over time. Review your current disability insurance coverage, update your will and medical directives to reflect your chronic illness needs, and consider establishing powers of attorney that specifically address healthcare and financial decisions during periods when symptoms may affect your judgment. This proactive planning ensures your wishes are respected and your family is protected from financial hardship related to your condition.'
  }
];</parameter>
